review_blob: Great sour beer that has opened new doors for me about what beer can be. Lovely carbonation.
Wow, Salty lemonade. Amazingly refreshing and easy to drink. i want to have this on a hot day.
Very strong grapefruit flavor. Very hoppy but not very bitter. Nice clean IPA that is easy to drink.
Rich and delicious beer with silky smooth finish. Really excellent beer after a nice meal.
Amazingly fresh and fruity. Really well hidden alcohol, Very nice and crisp double IPA.
Nice and refreshing low abv beer. Fresh and good tasting. Easy to drink. Enjoyable everyday beer
Super grapefruit aroma. Very pale and clear with nice foam. Very good flavor and nice balance. Great beer
Excellent beer for Nordic winters. Nice malty flavor and beautiful color. Firm and crisp bitterness.
This hop bomb has less aroma than others during this tasting session.  A bit murky in appearance also.  Flavor is good and drinkable.
Very fruity flavor. Not like other lagers I have had. This is interesting and enjoyable
Very easy drinking session beer. Fresh and delightful aroma and crisp and refreshing beer. Excellent
Wonderful coconut aroma and some tropical fruit. Very strong with interesting flavor. Finish is bitter.very good and unique beer.
Totally unique- sauna in a bottle. Nice birch aroma and taste. Light and refreshing.
Wow, great aroma, tropical fruit explosion! Expected some crazy bitterness but it is so well balanced and smooth...mmm yum.
Well balanced and smooth white IPA. Fruity and refreshing, very drinkable.
